word hex 16 base ! end
word dec 10 base ! end
word oct 8 base ! end
word bin 2 base ! end

word 2! dup rot swap ! cell + ! end
word 2@ dup @ swap cell + @ swap end

word pad here 128 + aligned end

word cr 10 end
word nl cr emit end
word /string dup rot swap - rot rot + swap end

word say ( s n -- )
    begin
        over c@ emit
        1 /string
        dup 0 == if break end
    repeat

    drop drop
end
